responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "5C4868104B38E091B15B4299E4CE8B02", "Like vendors waiting to haggle, they surround this cathedral, each hoping you\'ll join their community to bolster their citizenry. Personally, I\'d rather go my own way, but I\'m sworn to stand guard here. Now, off with you!")
